-
-## Current parity / debt map
-
-| Area | Current source or doc truth | V15 demo-spec expectation | Judgment |
-|---|---|---|---|
-| Demo-spec file exists | `ENGI_DEMO_SPEC_V15.md` now exists | demo realization must be documented separately | closed |
